Package: cpp11
Title: A C++11 Interface for R's C Interface
Version: 0.4.1
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Jim", family = "Hester", role = c("aut",
    "cre"), email = "jim.hester@rstudio.com", comment = c(ORCID =
    "0000-0002-2739-7082")), person(given = "Romain", family =
    "François", role = "ctb"), person(given = "Benjamin", family =
    "Kietzman", role = "ctb"), person(given = "RStudio", role =
    c("cph", "fnd")))
Description: Provides a header only, C++11 interface to R's C
    interface.  Compared to other approaches 'cpp11' strives to be safe
    against long jumps from the C API as well as C++ exceptions,
    conform to normal R function semantics and supports interaction
    with 'ALTREP' vectors.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://cpp11.r-lib.org, https://github.com/r-lib/cpp11
